title: The Teeth of the Tiger
creator: Maurice Leblanc
description: LibriVox recording of The Teeth of the Tiger, by Maurice Leblanc. Read by Cathy Barratt . Maurice Leblanc delivers another Arsene Lupin adventure set in World War I. (Summary by Cathy Barratt) For further information, including links to M4B audio book, online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
subject: LibriVox, audio book, fiction, WWI, mystery
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text

reviews.reviewbody:
This was my first exposure to Arsene Lupin - and what a climax to his career!

Excellent solo reading by Cathy Barratt for Librovox.
